author: etnu
msg: Applied second round of proxy refactoring for SHINDIG-371.
This is an extensive change to ProxyHandler, moving all makeRequest functionality to MakeRequestHandler.
A common base class that handles the shared functionality is introduced.
Many new tests added for both handlers.

This introduces a security improvement for the open proxy: all proxied files will now be served as file attachments. This can be an effective deterrent for anyone using the open proxy as a phishing vector while still retaining the desired functionality.
